data.description: (OPEN HOUSE 8/11 3-5, 8/12 12-2)*CASH ONLY* *OFFERS RECEIVED* This is a rare opportunity in Happy Valley. This is a heavy fixer with a lot of potential. The home has been smoked in and there is mold so please exercise caution when entering. The second kitchen and separate entrance in the lower level offer potential for multigen living or even an ADU. Fireplaces on each floor. Beautiful lot with western views. Great location with close proximity to shopping, schools, hospitals and freeways.
